		<title>16John Thomson (cont.)</title>
		<content> He was carried from the field to the  
 ambulance and rushed to the hospital. 
 John Thomson died 5 hours after the   
 match without regaining consciousness.
                                       
 20,000 flocked to Fife for John's     
 funeral. Cardenden was a mass of      
 flowers and awash with tears. He lies 
 buried in Bowhill Cemetary and each   
 year Glasgow Celtic fans come on a    
 pilgrimage to his grave on the 5th of 
 September.                            
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
